{
  "stem": "21437.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was horribly hard work because I was just presented-- I was presented-- I was given, you know, those disks, metal disks, and I had to bore holes into them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the holes had to be so accurate in the minutest detail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would have made a mistake, it would have meant treason, and it would have meant again punishment, you know, collective punishment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- So this is the way I worked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the beginning, I thought when I was asked if I did focus, I thought I did focus.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Focus means if you are-- if you are nurtured.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I was-- most of the time, you know, we just barely to-- to survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But all I did, it was focus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at night, that few minutes we whispered to one another, and we talked about and in detail, about how Homer, how-- And I realized then that-- that the inspiration I-- I-- if I am alive, I need, in whatever way, that bit of enrichment and inspiration has to come.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, again, you-- you reach deep within you, and you responded to somebody next to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- and you know what she said to me?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you want me to sing this to you, I will sing it to you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said to me, Rutka-- [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rutusch, ?] she said, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Rutusch, ?] I know that you-- you know, you remember still, as if you-- you were a child, that was a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Let's be children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Do you remember the French songs that you were taught that you-- I said, yes I do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So she said, sing them to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I said, how can sing them to you?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
